title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Robert Dole is way ahead, followed closely by his wife, Elizabeth Dole.” [Heard on WEEI-AM, Boston, Massachusetts, on 13 July 1988. Submitted by Ginny Crouse, Bookline, Massachusetts.]
